snippet.title: PARANORMAL RECORDS - OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
DEMO - 09.10.2023

RUS SUB

Paranormal Records is a story-driven psychological horror game. A unique storytelling experience from the perspective of a video camera. Feel like the host of a TV show about the paranormal and go to an abandoned psychiatric hospital.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2404960?beta=0
VK: https://vk.com/blackbalance_games
